{"tid":1327360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有否大麻藥用合法化的可能性？","createTime":"2019-07-17T14:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T06:40:25.000Z","uid":281198,"like":46,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7d1a75a4c04c3fb6fbfed8330e273905cb2a69","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n<br />\n海外許多國家已經慢慢改變對大麻的理解﹐從毒品為一種藥物／植物。的而且確﹐比起酒精及其他對腦部帶來負面影響的藥物，大麻本身沒有毒性﹐大麻什至為不少病患帶來舒緩效用。<br />\n<br />\n在人類歷史裡，大麻早在千年前就為人使用了，當時主要作為經濟和藥用作物。《神農本草經》與《本草綱目》亦有記載，李時珍認為整株大麻的根莖花葉果實皆有可用價值，但臨床醫學上則以麻子仁的使用為多。大麻的流傳程度，在17世紀中至19世紀初之間，藥用大麻更是美洲的通用貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據美國疾管局2013年的資料顯示，所有合法與非法藥物的使用者『死亡』統計。死亡率最高的是香菸 (48萬人/年) ＞ 酒精 (2.6萬人/年) ＞ 合法藥物 (2.2萬人/年) (例如：止痛藥、抗憂鬱藥......) ＞ &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.. ＞ 大麻 (0人/年)。 <br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n相信有幸點過的手足都會明白﹐<span style=\"color: green;\">大麻</span>帶畀人只有快樂與和平。除此以外﹐大麻同時也是一種文化﹐以及商機。不過下次再出post同大家傾。<br />\n<br />\n經年累月的誤解只會帶來更多無知與固執﹐你睇社會上幾撚多垃圾藍絲廢老牛屎佬就會明白。<br />\n<br />\n人必須突破框架﹐至少思想上要突破才會帶來整個社會的進步。同時﹐無知本身就是一種不自由﹐主要是由於一種錯誤的資訊傳遞。<br />\n<br />\n如果你都明白我講緊咩﹐我地就係同路人﹐一齊努力同身邊人帶起這個話題﹐傾多D，一傳十十傳百﹐盡力消除大家的誤解，一齊為大麻正名吧。love ＆ peace。<br />\n<br />\n最後﹐721，手足街上見。<br />\n<br />\n我無野講。"},{"pid":"da7b9ee21c8cfa1e4259360e4a1ed0dc4021dade","tid":1327360,"uid":141148,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"大麻係香港就係毒品 原罪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085eb336c117c998abd3fb8699568774a6ed52a7","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da7b9ee21c8cfa1e4259360e4a1ed0dc4021dade","tid":1327360,"uid":141148,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"大麻係香港就係毒品 原罪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"就係因為咁先至要拎出黎討論！"},{"pid":"7c67f47da3fffd8bee3ae35bd3c2a8113a9cc680","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ce2c54a2f66fdbf86308517765af44e64d0490e3","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"58cc0052d46de056e2d4cfdad3545652e56e71cf","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c0d5846fc36410e3ea34245446ab64c17cb14d1c","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab4c6502db925bd42b99af3f8aca9a6c3530f424","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e796f06639f868643679e71e0147839ea621a138","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"783cf821f030cc27aee84483689d90072fed6d45","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e06d1fc2f564aeed67305290290042fd42086a0a","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ff5f87d0ab2762825a6d137b4e370100c89f2430","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3056b07e664e80f32507a804d31c13691aa530b3","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"810317a2db8ac3d277ce39745f98cc1c661dc208","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1e1ea4b32771c3d5348635cb2a67e4ad67f3392","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2b1dbf5d9b23741f04865206cfcebf95d121894d","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0a1f704633d899cb3ed82fb606b931d0edc988d2","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d7fd03e5939c73d09d208349b39afd2f746de696","tid":1327360,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"唔立法會唔會諗住搞個遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4defb78c890d46631d5c5a138f321059a17aa13b","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7fd03e5939c73d09d208349b39afd2f746de696","tid":1327360,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"唔立法會唔會諗住搞個遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"謝謝回覆阿～<br />\n<br />\n當然要夠人數﹐即係民意基礎啦&hellip;咁我都唔係白痴﹐明白香港只係個經濟發展至上﹐但思想上好多人都保守到爆的社會。<br />\n<br />\n不過總要有人開始講﹐咁先傳到出去。能夠做到多少就做多少。<br />\n<br />\n如果你都明我講緊咩﹐希望可以一齊想辦法幫手啦。<br />\n<br />\n我無野講。"},{"pid":"c0fb20e3a4bfd3c33622fd68f96e700dae26e350","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:05:53.000Z","msg":"大麻不是毒品"},{"pid":"9d0dda4e10442e57975df6e2d3a627dd9cd951a8","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"大麻不是毒品"},{"pid":"98437fd3e996b212db42d6535e094c80022241a0","tid":1327360,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:15:08.000Z","msg":"大麻不是毒品"},{"pid":"76333fa858